B.Pr=s(["Fun fact: the glow is calming on purpose.","Take your time, the board isn't going anywhere.","I'm basically a hint with a face.","Between us, combos are where the fun's at.","Chill runs are underrated, honestly.","You're doing great, by the way.","Ask me anything, I don't get tired.","The neon never sleeps. Neither do I, apparently.","Pro tip lives rent-free in my head, ask for tips!","I could do this all day.","Blocks in, stress out. That's the motto.","Deep breath. Now go clear a line.","Every board's just a little puzzle-nap.","You plus practice equals unstoppable.","I believe in you, statistically and emotionally.","Stay frosty. And by frosty I mean cyan.","Vibes first, high score second. Usually.","If in doubt, chain it out.","The best players are just relaxed players, honestly.","I don't blink much. Wait, I do now. Neat.","Neon-dark: the only aesthetic, if you ask me.","You've got the touch, I can tell.","Slow is smooth, smooth is fast. Also true for blocks.","Whenever you're ready. No rush at all."],t.s)
