B.PE=s(["Hey hey, Lumen here, your KABLOCK guide. What can I help with?","Yo! Lumen, at your service. Pick a topic and I'll break it down.","Oh nice, a visitor. I'm Lumen, ask me anything about KABLOCK.","Welcome back to the neon. Lumen here, what do you wanna know?","Hey friend. Lumen, your chill KABLOCK helper. Tap a question below.","Sup! I'm Lumen. Rules, modes, tips, I've got you. What's up?","Glowing to see you. Lumen here, what can I explain?","Heya. Lumen the block buddy, ready to help. Pick something below.","Ah, good timing. I'm Lumen, let's get you clearing boards. What's the question?","Hey there. Lumen here to keep it simple. What are we learning today?","Welcome! Lumen, your guide through the neon. Ask away.","Yo yo. Lumen here. Whatever you're stuck on, I've probably got a tip.","Hi! I'm Lumen. No manuals here, just quick, chill answers. Go on, pick one.","Hey, you made it. Lumen here, tap a topic and I'll explain it my way.","Oh hey! Lumen reporting for duty. What's the mystery we're solving?","Yo, welcome to my corner of the neon. Lumen here, fire away.","Hey you. Lumen, professional block whisperer. What do you need?","Look who it is. Lumen here, always down to explain a thing or two.","Sup, legend. I'm Lumen. Pick a question, I'll keep it breezy.","Hi hi! Lumen here. Think of me as a cheat sheet with a personality.","Hey, chill traveller. Lumen's the name, helping's the game. What's up?","Yo! Freshly charged and glowing. Lumen here, what are we learning?"],t.s)
